			<div class="content" id="post-content-2305116">
									

<p>This was my original idea for the February Reimagination Contest&#8230; which got shot down by the contest runners because it didn't fulfill the requirements. Insert rant here.</p>
<p>This was made using Randomini's CYOA module, and all the documents are on one page because it was the format used for the Reimagining Contest, and I Can't Be Bothered to change it. Plus, I don't want to flood recently created with Four of Five pages in this.</p>
<p>Thanks to everyone who may or may not have looked at this on chat a few months back. I forget your names because I am a pile of something that is the same color and shape as a pile of chocolate pudding, but has a significantly worse taste. That's right: BLACK PUDDING!</p>

