<p>Super cool! The Colossus (<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-2406" target="_blank">SCP-2406</a>) was also built with Orichalcum but went by an estimated admixture of metals because I felt the Foundation wouldn't use the term, so aimed for the hypothesized materials that would be part of that alloy.</p>
<p>I've actually wanted to do something with the Church of Maxwell - despite their modern trappings, I feel they are a return to the goals of the original church, a broader passion for technological progress. Steam and gears but one step in our journey to perfection:)</p>
<p>Err, sorry, rambling. Anyway. Really enjoyed this. In my mind, MEKHANE has no set gender - being a purely mechanical entity, but referred to as he or she as anthropomorphism - humanizing something otherwise quite alien from us.</p>

							</div>

								
					
